AssetFeatureResponse

Asset Response as a GeoJSon Feature with Asset properties

Field Required Type Description

geometry

optional GeoJsonPoint See GeoJsonPoint for more information.

properties

optional AssetResponse See AssetResponse for more information.

type

optional string

the Geojson Type (only 'Feature')

The allowed values include: and Feature
